### Version of Hardhat

2.14.3

### What happened?

vyper already supports 0.3.9, but hardhat-vyper can't it be compile and downloaded 0.3.9

<img width="600" alt="image" src="https://github.com/NomicFoundation/hardhat/assets/40197424/81923928-5d81-4e2e-8472-628eda682e80">


